# PattaFlow — Full Codebase Overview

## Project Summary
**PattaFlow** is an AI-powered **Tamil Nadu land record verification system**. Given an Encumbrance Certificate (EC) PDF and a set of Sale Deed PDFs, it:
1. Extracts and parses the EC using Google Gemini
2. Matches the EC entries to the provided sale deed PDFs
3. Extracts detailed metadata from each sale deed via Gemini
4. Generates an interactive property ownership hierarchy/lineage tree
5. Cross-validates each sale deed against the EC using Gemini as a forensic auditor
6. Presents all results in a React frontend with PDF preview, annotation, and AI chat

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | React 18, TypeScript, Vite, TailwindCSS, Shadcn/Radix UI |
| **State/Routing** | React Router v6, TanStack Query v5 |
| **Maps** | OpenLayers ([ol](file:///d:/Master_legal_AI/Server/api/validate/hierarchy_generator.py#221-236)) |
| **Flow Visualization** | ReactFlow v11 |
| **PDF Handling** | pdfjs-dist, react-pdf-highlighter |
| **Backend** | Python 3, FastAPI, Uvicorn |
| **AI/LLM** | Google Gemini API (`gemini-2.5-flash`, `gemini-2.5-flash-lite`) |
| **PDF Parsing** | pypdf, PyMuPDF (fitz) |
| **External APIs** | TNGIS EC API, TNGIS Land Info API |

